stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Monitoring
    
    Monitoring --> Warning: Threshold exceeded
    Warning --> Critical: No response in 5m
    Critical --> Escalated: No response in 15m
    Escalated --> Resolved: Issue fixed
    
    Monitoring --> Resolved: Auto-recovery
    Warning --> Resolved: Manual fix
    Critical --> Resolved: Team intervention
    Escalated --> Resolved: Management involved
    
    note right of Warning
        Level 1: Automated alert
        Notify: On-call engineer
        Response: 15 minutes
    end note
    
    note right of Critical
        Level 2: Team alert
        Notify: Entire team
        Response: 5 minutes
    end note
    
    note right of Escalated
        Level 3: Management alert
        Notify: Department head
        Response: Immediate
    end note